              "name": "Component/MEGA Wordmark",
              "context": "Hero MEGA wordmark — scroll-driven assembly. Pinned section for 1800px of scroll. Phase 1 (0-900px): 4 letter paths (M,E,G,A) fly in from off-screen right with stagger 0.25s. Behind them, an outline placeholder ghost (cloned letter paths, fill=hero-bg, stroke=text @0.32 opacity) wrapped in a group at opacity 0.32 to prevent alpha-stacking artifacts. Placeholders fade out individually as letters land. Phase 2 (900-1800px): 4 microcopy paths (Make/Earth/Great/Again) start at scale:20 opacity:0, pop to opacity:1 instantly when MEGA done, then shrink to scale:1 over remaining scroll. Letters and microcopy use power3.out / power2.out / scrub:0.6.",
