          "id": "l8EIe",
          "name": "motionSec",
          "context": "Motion tokens (UI-level transitions) + scroll-driven animations layered on top via GSAP/ScrollTrigger. Scroll choreography (live): (1) Hero MEGA assembly — pinned 1800px, letters fly in from right (stagger 0.25s, power3.out) Phase 1 [0-900px], microcopy zooms scale 20→1 (stagger 0.08s, power2.out) Phase 2 [900-1800px], scrub 0.6s. (2) Mission body — SplitText word-by-word reveal, opacity/y/blur scrubbed top 85%→top 35%, scrub 0.4s. (3) Project rows — sticky 100vh category header + cards lagging at yPercent:75 → 0 across viewport traversal (scrub 0.4s). (4) Category bg video parallax — yPercent 8 → -8 (scrub: true). (5) Project Overlay — back.out(1.4) panel scale-in with scrim+blur, 0.45s entrance, 0.22s exit. (6) Footer MEGA! — rotateX 0 → -360 backflip, 1.4s power2.inOut, fires once on viewport enter at top 80%.",
