                  "fill": "$ink",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "Project Plastic seeks to create a marine cleanup initiative designed to remove plastic waste from the ocean with minimal disruption to marine ecosystems. It uses a vortex-based collection system that mimics natural currents to guide debris into a capture zone—no nets, no entanglement risk. A grace window before surface skimming allows marine life to escape safely, while a network of subsurface sensors and aerial drones monitors the operation in real time to further prevent bycatch.",
