                  "type": "frame",
                  "id": "ldN5g",
                  "name": "Component/MEGA Vertical Wordmark",
                  "context": "Footer MEGA! vertical wordmark. Animation: the '!' (vmMain stem path + vmDot circle) does a true 3D backflip — rotateX from 0 to -360 — when #footer-branding enters viewport at top 80%, fires once per page load. 1.4s duration, power2.inOut ease. Pivot at svg-unit center (210, 125). Requires perspective:1200px on parent + transform-style:preserve-3d on the SVG. CSS transform applied via gsap onUpdate (GSAP's SVG transform attribute is 2D-only).",
                  "reusable": true,
                  "width": 234,
                  "height": 244,
                  "fill": "#00000000",
                  "layout": "none",
